thought.text:
I see that `comment_span` (which is `comment.content_span()`) is used extensively in the builder — not just for `DisableRuleComment.span`, but also for:
- `disabledRule` `comment_span` field (line 405, 418, 453, 466)
- The `interval` grouping in `collect_unused_disable_comments`
